\r\n树莓派W+Respeaker 2 Mics \r\n具体说明下问题\r\n昨天安装过一次因为声卡配置问题今天重新刷了一次最新的4月8日的系统，\r\n新装以后先装的声卡驱动，是按照大神的声卡选配装的\r\n测试录音播放无异常后，脚本安装了\r\n```\r\npi@raspberrypi:~ $ arecord -d 3 temp.wav  # 测试录音3秒\r\nRecording WAVE 'temp.wav' : Unsigned 8 bit, Rate 8000 Hz, Mono\r\npi@raspberrypi:~ $ aplay temp.wav # 播放录音看看效果\r\nPlaying WAVE 'temp.wav' : Unsigned 8 bit, Rate 8000 Hz, Mono\r\n```\r\n出现No module named 'xxx’，按照脚本wiki\r\n`sudo pip3 install -r requirements.txt `\r\n后正常启动，但无法唤醒，再检测声卡是录播又异常了？\r\n执行\r\n`sudo wget http://wukong-install.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/changeSource.sh && sudo chmod 777 changeSource.sh &&./changeSource.sh`\r\n后问题依旧\r\n```\r\n.asoundrc\r\npcm.!default {\r\n    type asym\r\n    playback.pcm {\r\n        type plug\r\n        slave.pcm \"hw:1,0\"\r\n    }\r\n    capture.pcm {\r\n        type plug\r\n        slave.pcm \"hw:1,0\"\r\n    }        \r\n}\r\n\r\nctl.!default {\r\n    type hw\r\n    card 1\r\n}\r\n```\r\n于是找到http://wiki.seeedstudio.com/ReSpeaker_2_Mics_Pi_HAT/\r\n```\r\n$ sudo apt update\r\n$ sudo apt install audacity\r\n$ audacity                      // 运行 audacity\r\n```\r\n用audacity默认设备检测监听无声，设置seeed-2mic-voicecard正常？却不知道怎么设备才能被wukong使用，请大神们帮忙？感激不尽！","closed_by":{"login":"Myeeoo","id":49667129,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5NjY3MTI5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49667129?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo","html_url":"https://github.com/Myeeoo","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Myeeoo/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https